    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<strong>Explore an infinite amount of pixelated worlds in this adventure sandbox game, and find villages, enemy camps, and quests along your journey!</strong><br><br>In Pixeplorer, you spawn into a procedurally generated world with only a sword and a set of basic armor. Your task? <i>Explore.</i> Trek through grasslands, savannas, deserts and more to collect resources, which then you can use to upgrade your items and fight enemies with. <br><br>Will you get lost in the game's boundless biomes collecting trees and fighting enemy hordes? Or, will you find a village and change the tides of battle, allowing you to sweep through fiercer enemy outposts? <strong>The choice is all yours in Pixeplorer.</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GAME FEATURES:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Infinite procedurally generating worlds, ranging from 512 x 512 tiles up to 2048 x 2048 tiles each<br></li><li> Enemy outposts and cave systems for intense combat, with 7 unique different enemy types total<br></li><li> Villages filled with NPCs and options to upgrade items<br></li><li>Trackable quest system to use resources and get powerful loot<br></li><li> ... And much more! </li></ul>",
